<mvc:View controllerName="sap.ui.demo.basicTemplate.controller.Home" displayBlock="true" xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:uxap="sap.uxap" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" xmlns:layout="sap.ui.layout">
    <uxap:ObjectPageLayout id="ObjectPageLayout" showTitleInHeaderContent="true" showEditHeaderButton="true" editHeaderButtonPress="handleEditBtnPress" upperCaseAnchorBar="false">
        <uxap:footer />
        <uxap:headerContent>
            <FlexBox wrap="Wrap">
                <Avatar class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd" src="./img/ich.jpg" displaySize="L" />

                <layout:VerticalLayout class="sapUiSmallMarginBeginEnd">
                    <Link text="+49 151 688 06 766" />
                    <Link text="lukas_rausch@gmx.de" />
                </layout:VerticalLayout>

                <layout:HorizontalLayout class="sapUiSmallMarginBeginEnd">
                    <Image src="./test-resources/sap/uxap/images/linkedin.png" />
                    <Image src="./test-resources/sap/uxap/images/Twitter.png" class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin" />
                </layout:HorizontalLayout>

                <layout:VerticalLayout class="sapUiSmallMarginBeginEnd">
                    <Image src="./img/twitter.png" class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin" />
                    <Avatar src="./img/github.png" class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin" />
                    <Image src="./img/linkedin.png" class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin" />
                    <Avatar src="./img/xing.png" class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin" />
                </layout:VerticalLayout>

                <layout:VerticalLayout class="sapUiSmallMarginBeginEnd">
                    <VBox>
                        <Label text="Erreichte Ziele" />
                        <ProgressIndicator percentValue="34" displayValue="30%" />
                    </VBox>
                </layout:VerticalLayout>

                <layout:VerticalLayout class="sapUiSmallMarginBeginEnd">
                    <Label text="Fulda, DE" />
                </layout:VerticalLayout>
            </FlexBox>
        </uxap:headerContent>
        <uxap:headerTitle>
            <uxap:ObjectPageDynamicHeaderTitle>
                <uxap:breadcrumbs>
                    <Breadcrumbs currentLocationText="Die Seite wurde mit OpenUi5 entworfen" />
                </uxap:breadcrumbs>
                <uxap:expandedHeading>
                    <HBox>
                        <Title text="Lukas Rausch" wrapping="true" />
                        <ObjectMarker type="Favorite" class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin" />
                    </HBox>
                </uxap:expandedHeading>

                <uxap:snappedHeading>
                    <FlexBox fitContainer="true" alignItems="Center">
                        <Avatar src="./img/ich.jpg" class="sapUiTinyMarginEnd" />
                        <Title text="Lukas Rausch" wrapping="true" />
                    </FlexBox>
                </uxap:snappedHeading>

                <uxap:expandedContent>
                    <Text text="Senior UI Entwickler" />
                </uxap:expandedContent>

                <uxap:snappedContent>
                    <Text text="Senior UI Entwickler" />
                </uxap:snappedContent>

                <uxap:snappedTitleOnMobile>
                    <Title text="Senior UI Entwickler" />
                </uxap:snappedTitleOnMobile>
            </uxap:ObjectPageDynamicHeaderTitle>
        </uxap:headerTitle>
        <uxap:landmarkInfo />
        <uxap:sections />
    </uxap:ObjectPageLayout>
</mvc:View>
